Who’s ready? The pack is back in Teen Wolf: The Movie 
streaming January 26 
on #ParamountPlus! #TeenWolfMovie

This show, these castmates, the crew, this character and the man that started it all, collectively and collaboratively influenced my life so heavily. 

I started doing conventions around the world back in my #SG-1 days and Teen Wolf grew those experiences of meeting extended family members exponentially. One of my favorite things about our job. There’s no show without family. 

I’ve missed key moments throughout the years, but that doesn’t and can’t erase the impactful moments shared over months of working and years of just being together. 

We are family ❤️

Hope y’all enjoy the movie as much as we enjoyed making it for y’all. 

January 26th 
2 DAYS AWAY
Only on @paramountplus

My good friend @chrissalgardo new company @atwaterskincare and  @ducatiusa have partnered to benefit @rxart who have already helped more than 3 million children since 2000, by transforming children’s hospital settings into engaging and powerfully healing environments through visual art. 

The partnership introduces the Limited Edition Clean Impact AXD1 Body Scrub and Cleansing Bar. 

So if you’re interested in clean, nontoxic, beegan, sulfate-free, cruelty-free, 100% sustainable skin care, and in supporting the mission of @rxart to help children heal through visual art then grab one of these bars at atwaterskin.com and Nordstrom.

Super excited to announce that the family’s getting together for the high school reunion on October 26-29, 2023. And you’re invited! The event will be taking place at Costly Mill in Conyers, Georgia

Unlike maybe your actual high school reunion you aren’t going to want to miss this! So go to BeaconHillsHigh.com (LINK IN BIO) or to Instagram, Facebook and TikTok at @SuperFanCons also for more information. See you at the Beacon Hills High School Reunion!

Wishing one of the brightest lights in the world a very Happy Birthday. This place can feel very divisive and detrimental lately but @echriqui shines a beacon of hope and love and I count myself lucky to receive not just those qualities, but her wisdom and bravery as well. Happy birthday my soul sister. May all your wishes for love and hope triumph and be felt across these turbulent waves. 
Love you Manni ❤️
